CASES DISPOSED OF IN VACATION.

No. 184. Hans Hohner v. Francis P. Garvan, as Alien Property Custodian, et al.

Appeal from the District Court of the United States for the Southern District of New York. August 21, 1920. Dismissed pursuant to the twenty-eighth rule. Mr. A. W. Lafferty for appellant. The Attorney General for appellees.
